# in but `function.name` never arrives. When `finish_reason: tool_calls` lands
# the choice aggregator calls _ToolCallAggregator.ensure_ended(), which is
# expected to:
#   1. emit a late ToolCallStartEvent with name='unknown' (warn-logged)
#   2. flush any buffered args with the synthetic name
#   3. emit ToolCallEndEvent
